This class is responsible for the magement of FS-UAE Gui.

detaileddescription.para: In this class are defined all the variables for the correct management of all types of settings possible to run FS-UAE. We have also introduced some secondary features for FS-UAE but not for the end user such as saving and loading configurations, the possibility of refreshing the gui and reporting bugs.
